  "title": "Projects Executive",
  "description": "<h2><u><strong>JOB DESCRIPTION</strong></u></h2><ul><li>Supervise the entire project management section to ensure smooth operation to all undertaken projects.</li></ul><ul><li>To carry out Single Line Drawing, EC Drawing, requires coordination with client.</li></ul><ul><li>Work closely with technical, logistic in planning, coordinating and implementing project plans according to contracted schedules.</li></ul><ul><li>Develop detailed task and resource allocation plans and schedules for project development and implementation phase.</li></ul><ul><li>Co-ordinate internally with the logistic department and external 3rd party logistic forwarder for shipping of goods</li></ul><h2><u><strong>REQUIREMENTS</strong></u></h2><ol><li>Candidates must possess at least a diploma in any field.</li><li>Knowledge of Microsoft Word/Excel and IT Skills are preferred.</li><li>Candidates with Autocad background will have an added advantage</li><li>Candidates with experience in the marine industry will have an added advantage</li><li>Willing to accept challenges to a wider job responsibility.</li><li>Must possess good communication, inter-personal and project management skills.</li></ol><p>Interested candidates please email your resume to career@cantrade.com.sg<br />\nTo facilitate the recruitment process, please include your <u><strong>expected salary, last drawn salary, reason for leaving past employment and notice period </strong></u>in your resume. <br />\nWe regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates will be notified about their applications.</p>",
